Real Estate listings held by brokers other than Zillow, Inc. are marked with the IDX Logo. All data in this web site is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed.

data.description: Check out this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath residence nestled in Tanglewood Estates! Boasting numerous details throughout including a spacious open floor plan, granite counter tops, updated tile in the bathrooms, high privacy back fence. The backyard showcases a covered patio complemented by an above-ground pool perfect for entertaining guests!  Don't miss your chance to view this home. Call to schedule your showing today!
